                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d411">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Ornelas</persName> to Señor
                            <persName type="to">Cayetano Romero</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San Antonio, Tex.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-12-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 14, 1892</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Col. Ceron telegraphs me as follows: “Sixteen Mexican soldiers, captured on the
                    10th and brought over by the raiders, are imprisoned at San Ignacio, Tex.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">P. Ornelas.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
